summary: A tough looking male nord preset, does not overwrite any other preset.
descriptionHtml:
A tough looking male nord preset, does not overwrite any other preset.

To change to this face you simply download the file and put it on your Skyrim/data folder, then you make sure that the .esp file is activated in your skyrim launcher or similar program.

I am wearing Einherjar armor in the screenshots, get his awesome mod here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10295

To change to this preset on an already started character, you open the console in the game(tilde key) and type \"showracemenu\", then you change to the 11th preset on the preset slider.

WARNING!
This preset is recommended to be used with a new character, if you change to this on an old character, make sure she/he already IS a nord, if you change race using the mentioned command, your stats will change.
author: envelope91
